            "text": ". \"If it had not been the Lord who was on our side when men rose up against us, then they had swallowed us up quick, when their wrath was kindled against us; then the waters had overwhelmed us, the stream had gone over our soul; then the proud waters had gone over our soul;\" see ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Psalm 69:1",
            "children": []
          },
          {
