        "text": "ὁ τοιοῦτος",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", the man of that description, the name by which St Paul always denotes the offender. See note on ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
