          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "swallowed up",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] Some commentators have supposed that St Paul here meant apostasy or suicide. But he designedly leaves the result indefinite. It is impossible to foresee what will become of a man overwhelmed with excessive sorrow.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
